PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1992-1950 that permit THE TORONTO HARBOUR COMMISSIONERS to sell (a) Parts 1, 2, 3, 5 and 10, Plan 64R-14473, to the City of Toronto, and Parts 7 and 9 to either Marathon Realty Company Limited or Southtown Inc., and (b) Parts 6 and 58, Plan 64R-13323 to either the City, Marathon, Southtown, Centre Court Stadium Inc., Centre Court Limited Partnership or Air Canada.
